	* added collect timing statistics for cpu and average response time
	* fixed problem with VM_Free crash

2011-07-11 Dusan Jocic <dusanjocic@msn.com>
	* Updated libpng library 
		+ compiled it with x64 support
	* Updated zlib library
		+ compiled it with x64 support
	* Added x64 Visual Studio configuration build based on ioQuake
		+ Entire engine is now x64 compatible
		+ x64bit mods can be loaded
