	* Replaced static library cURL library from engine to dynamic library
		+ Game required now libcurl(d).dll/.so/.dylib in root folder to work
	* Added the date and time of compilation to the version string
	* Added possibility to connect on IRC Chatroom
	* Added SWITCHSTRING to allow strings to be used in switch cases
	* Rewrited NET_IPSocket
		- changed *err to netadrtype_t type
	* Added COM_Parse3 and COM_ParseExt3

