		+ Game required now freetype6.dll/.so/.dylib in root folder to work
	* Added dynamic OpenSSL libraries
		+ Game required now libeay32.dll/.so/.dylib in root folder to work
	* Added missing VectorLerp in q_shared.h

2011-06-29 Dusan Jocic <dusanjocic@msn.com>

	* Changed several VM_NATIVE
		- system should interpreted virtual machine to choose what file to be loaded
		- good for LLVM and QVM (both byte code)
			+ If image ends in .qvm it will be interpreted, otherwise it will attempt to load as a system dll

