	* Little cleanup in q_shared.h
	* Moved #define MAC_STATIC from q_shared.h to q_platform.h
	* Replaced CPUSTRING with ARCH_STRING
	* Moved compiled files in x32 folder for Win32 and to x64 if solution configuration is set to x64, GLEW x64 version is build as GLEW64(d).dll
