	* Added d in SDL name for debug build (x86 and x64)
	* Added LUA 5.1 64bit files

2011-06-18 Dusan Jocic <dusanjocic@msn.com>

	* Removed command "userinfo" because it does nothing
	* Forgot to include MySQL folder in game VS2010 project
	* separated IP into IP4 and IP6 in MySQL tables
	* Moved OW_Init() (MySQL Init) from SV_ServerSpawn() to CL_Init()
		- Better that MySQL be initialized on application start
		- Separated OW_MySQL_CreateTable from OW_Init() and added it in CL_Init()
			to be initialized after OW_Init()
	* moved OW_Shutdown (MySQL Shutdown) from SV_SpawnServer() and SV_Shutdown() to CL_Shutdown()
		- Client should disconnect from MySQL database only at application quit/exit
	* changed QKEY name from "etxreal" to "openwolf"
	* Added ARCH_STRING for checking x86/x86_64 files
	* Added X64 in solution configutration
		- It copy all includes and files from Win32 solution
		- Just changed target machine to Machine/X64 (/MACHINE:X64)
		- It still need all 64bit modules and includes (BROKEN AT THIS MOMENT)
	* Fixed compiling ETMAIN with x64 solution configuration
		- moved 32-bit files in new BIN/x32 folder
			+ cgame_mp_x86.dll, qagame_mp_x86.dll, ui_mp_x86.dll
		- after compiling with x64 it will create new BIN/x64 folder and there
			+ cgame_mp_x86_64.dll, qagame_mp_x86_64.dll, ui_mp_x86_64.dll

