2010-08-24 Robert Beckebans <trebor_7@users.sourceforge.net>

	* Added tangent space calculations to mdm models.
	* Rewrote Tess_UpdateVBOs().
	* Fixed a bug in R_CalcTangentSpaceFast that caused randomized tangent spaces on .md3 models.
	* Changed "buildcubemaps" command to render cubemaps for each BSP leave origin instead for every lightgrid point.
	* Fixed deformVertexes bulge on entities.
	* Renamed r_ext_texture_compression to r_ext_compressed_textures for compatibility with the ui code.
	* Added missing check for the lightmap shader stage keyword.
	* Fixed more rendering problems with implicit materials.
	* Optimized GLimp_LogComment.
	* Added GLIntercept 1.0 Beta 00 configuration file configured to log GL_GREMEDY_string_marker calls.
	* Changed GLimp_LogComment to use GL_GREMEDY_string_marker.

2010-08-23 Robert Beckebans <trebor_7@users.sourceforge.net>

	* Added animated camera film grain.
	* Fixed loading of lightmaps.
	* Changed OpenGL 3.x context initialization to be optional because wglCreateContextAttribsARB likes to crash after a vid_restart.
	If you want to start the renderer with the OpenGL 3.2 core profile then you need to set r_glCoreProfile to 1 at startup.
	* Some changes that allows the renderer to use OpenGL 3.2 with a core profile.

